  <zone type="main">
    <line>tence, <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">But</del>
        <add place="superlinear">but</add>
      </mod> that my vow was heard and I</line>
    <line>was reserved for vengeance – The laughter</line>
    <line>died away <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">and</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">when</add>
      </mod> a well known and <del rend="strikethrough">detested</del></line>
    <line>abhorred voice apparently close to my ear ad</line>
    <line>dressed me in an audible whisper – I am sa</line>
    <line>tisfied, <del rend="strikethrough">it said,</del> miserable wretch, you have</line>
    <line>determined to live &amp; I am satisfied – I darted</line>
    <line>towards the place from which the <del rend="strikethrough">moon</del> sound</line>
    <line>proceeded but the <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">wretch</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear">villain</add></del>
        <add place="sublinear" resp="#pbs">devil</add>
      </mod> eluded my grasp.</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">When</del> suddenly the broard disk of the moon</line>
    <line>arose and shone fully upon <delSpan rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c57-0159.01"
        next="#c57-0159.02" spanTo="#c57-0159.03"/>the dæmon</line>
    <line>who fled.<anchor xml:id="c57-0159.03"/>
      <mod xml:id="c57-0159.02" prev="#c57-0159.01" type="additions" resp="#pbs">
        <add place="intralinear">his ghastly &amp; distorted shape, as he fled with</add>
        <!--I assume this is pbs, though the scholar doesn't indicate it-->
        <add><ptr target="#c57-0159.04"/></add>
      </mod></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line>I persued <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">him;</add>– &amp; for many months
      this</line>
    <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
    <line><add><ptr target="#c57-0159.05"/></add> has been my task. Guided by a slight clue</line>
    <line>I <del rend="double-strike">w</del> followed the windings of the Rhone</line>
    <line>but vainly – The mediterranean appeared</line>
    <line>and by a strange chance I saw the fiend</line>
    <line>enter by night &amp; hide himself in a vessel</line>
    <line>bound for the black sea – I followed him <add><ptr target="#c57-0159.06"/></add></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">Along the</del> Amidst the wilds of Tartary &amp;</line>
    <line>Russia although he still <mod>
        <del rend="double-strike">escaped</del>
        <add resp="#pbs" place="superlinear">evaded</add>
      </mod> me</line>
    <line>I have ever followed in his track – Some</line>
    <line>times the peasants scared by his horrid</line>
    <line>Apparition informed me of his path</line>
    <line>Sometimes he himself who feared that</line>
    <line>if I lost all trace I should despair &amp; die</line>
    <line>often left some mark to guide me –The</line>
    <line>snows descended on my head &amp; I saw the <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">mark</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">print</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line>of his huge step on the white plain –To</line>
    <line>you <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">are fast</add> enterring on life, &amp; care <add
        place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">is new to you &amp; <add><metamark>✗</metamark><ptr
            target="#c57-0159.07"/></add></add> how can</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">I describe</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">you understand</add>
      </mod> what I have felt &amp; still feel.</line>
    <line>which I was Cold, want &amp; <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">thirst</del>
        <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add>
        <add place="superlinear">fatigue</add>
      </mod> were <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">my</del>
        <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">the</add>
      </mod> least pains</line>
    <line><add><ptr target="#c57-0159.08"/></add>I was cursed by some devil &amp; bore about</line>
    <line>with me my eternal Hell – Yet still a</line>
    <line>spirit of good followed &amp; directed my steps</line>
  </zone>
  <zone type="left_margin">
    <addSpan xml:id="c57-0159.04" spanTo="#c57-0159.09"/>
    <line>more than</line>
    <line>mortal speed.</line>
    <anchor xml:id="c57-0159.09"/>
  </zone>
  <zone type="left_margin">
    <line><add xml:id="c57-0159.05">pursuit</add></line>
  </zone>
  <zone type="left_margin">
    <addSpan xml:id="c57-0159.06" spanTo="#c57-0159.10"/>
    <line>I knew the</line>
    <line>vessel in which</line>
    <line>he was concealed</line>
    <line>&amp; he escaped me</line>
    <line>I know not</line>
    <line>how.</line><anchor xml:id="c57-0159.10"/>
  </zone>
  <zone type="left_margin">
    <line><add xml:id="c57-0159.07"><metamark>✗</metamark> agony unknown</add></line>
  </zone>
  <zone type="left_margin">
    <addSpan xml:id="c57-0159.08" spanTo="#c57-0159.11"/>
    <line>which I was</line>
    <line>destined to endure;</line>
    <anchor xml:id="c57-0159.11"/>
  </zone>
